    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>            Your guardian devil hopes that you’ve been put at ease by better understanding the administration's perspective regarding these highly necessary construction activities. If there’s one lesson here that I strongly believe and hope to impart, it’s this—you’re not important enough, so stop complaining. </p>
<p><i>Your guardian devil is commissioning a 100-foot statue of Miley Cyrus riding a wrecking ball for the new BC plaza. </i></p>
<p> <br></p>

